      <title>英国生育率降至1938年有记录以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/uk-fertility-rate-sinks-to-lowest-since-records-began-in-1938</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于经济压力和更广泛的社会转变使年轻人不愿建立家庭，英格兰威尔士的生育率在 2023 年降至历史最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/uk-fertility-rate-sinks-to-lowest-since-records-began-in-1938</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 15:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
